data.description: The note for this home is assumable at an incredible rate of 2.25 % for a balance of ~$1,130,000 as of 10/20/2023. This incredible interest rate can save buyers thousands of dollars monthly in interest.     Situated in the gated community of Summit Ridge near Medina Lake, this thoughtfully designed contemporary residence offers captivating vistas of the Texas Hill Country with a sprawling 5,554 sq.ft.. of living space.      Soaring ceilings, custom lighting and an abundance of natural light stream through oversized windows highlighting luxury details throughout. The home includes multiple living spaces, a study offering beautiful tile flooring, a private gym, full wet bar with a sink, dishwasher, ice maker and stand-up 150 bottle wine fridge, dual utility rooms with washer/dryer connections and a pet grooming station, an attached 3-car garage as well as a detached 4-car garage with mini-split AC, epoxy floors, secure locks, and insulated roll up doors, one oversized to fit an RV.     The chef's kitchen, features a double island with a breakfast bar, top-of-the-line Jenn Air stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry with lighting and a gas cook top complete with a pot filler.      The expansive main living area features a beautiful fireplace and folding glass doors that open up to the outdoor oasis.         The primary suite is a luxurious retreat, offering breathtaking outdoor views, a cozy fireplace, generous walk-in closet and an en suite bathroom adorned with an oversized vanity, stylish tile, a soaking tub and a walk-in glass shower with dual shower heads.         The outdoor living space is an entertainer's dream, offering a pergola kitchen with stainless appliances, a bar top for casual dining and a heated waterfall swimming pool with a built-in table. Additionally, there's a poolside out-house with two restrooms and two fully functional showers for ultimate convenience.
